\hypertarget{steps}{%
\paragraph{Steps:}\label{steps}}

\begin{enumerate}
\def\labelenumi{\arabic{enumi}.}
\tightlist
\item
  Preprocessed data using AFNI (preproc\_funcs.sh) and aligned to MNI
  coordinates using the \textbf{MNI 152} and \textbf{glasser} brain
  parcellation maps for each individual subject (align\_to\_MNI.sh).
\item
  Ran the ROI searchlight decoding for each of individuals for each
  question:
\end{enumerate}

\begin{itemize}
\tightlist
\item
  Those are presented sequentially below and labeled by the question
\end{itemize}

\begin{enumerate}
\def\labelenumi{\arabic{enumi}.}
\setcounter{enumi}{2}
\tightlist
\item
  Averaged across individuals within each ROI for each question.
\item
  Mapped the averaged accuracy for each question
\end{enumerate}
